OL,3,CMan arrested for allegedly spitting at
OL,4,Cpolice during Donaldson court hearing
OL,6,FPolice have confirmed that a man has
OL,7,Fbeen arrested for allegedly spitting
OL,8,Fon an officer during Sir Jeffrey
OL,9,FDonaldson's court hearing in Newry.
OL,11,FThe 37-year-old was later released
OL,12,Fpending further enquiries.
OL,14,FPolice said they are also
OL,15,Finvestigating comments made online
OL,16,Fabout the high-profile court case to
OL,17,Fdetermine if any offences have been
OL,18,Fcommitted.
