OL,3,CMan arrested for allegedly spitting at
OL,4,Cpolice during Donaldson court hearing
OL,6,FFormer DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,7,FDonaldson was appeared in person for
OL,8,Fthe first time at Newry courthouse
OL,9,Fafter his arrest and charged for
OL,10,Falleged historical sexual offences
OL,11,Fincluding rape and gross indecency.
OL,13,FHe faces a total of 11 charges,
OL,14,Fallegedly dating back as far as 1985
OL,15,Fand up to 2006.
OL,17,FHe has previously indicated that he
OL,18,Fwill strenuously contest the charges.
