OL,3,CMan arrested for allegedly spitting at
OL,4,Cpolice during Donaldson court hearing
OL,6,FHis wife, Lady Eleanor Donaldson, also
OL,7,Fappeared at court, facing charges of
OL,8,Faiding and abetting Sir Jeffrey's
OL,9,Falleged offences.
OL,11,FChaotic scenes unfolded outside Newry
OL,12,Fcourt house on Wednesday when the
OL,13,Fcouple arrived and left separately
OL,14,Fwith members of the public vying for
OL,15,Fposition to see the defendants.
OL,17,FMembers of the local, national and
OL,18,Finternational press were also in
OL,19,Fattendance with a heavy police
OL,20,Fpresence throughout the hearing.
