OL,3,CMan arrested for allegedly spitting at
OL,4,Cpolice during Donaldson court hearing
OL,6,FPolice have also said that they are
OL,7,Finvestigating footage posted online by
OL,8,Fmembers of the public following the
OL,9,Fcourt hearing.J"We would also again
OL,10,Fremind all members of the public that
OL,11,Fspeculation about the identity of
OL,12,Fvictims or the circumstances
OL,13,Fsurrounding this case is illegal and
OL,14,Fwe are actively investigating those
OL,15,Fwho are perpetrating this online and
OL,16,Fdeciding on the most appropriate
OL,17,Faction to take.J"This type of
OL,18,Fspeculation along with defamatory
OL,19,Fcomments made about the defendants
OL,20,Fcould have a seriously negative impact
OL,21,Fon criminal justice proceedings."
